_sText: This is a complete map of my room, without all the props of course.. It is a bit blocky, but I'm sure you won't notice it that much. There is alot of places you can go, like under the bed, in the dresser, in the closet, ect. It took me about 9 hours, not including all the bug fixing to get this map built. Any amount of players is good for this map. No flaming, just constructive feedback please. Enjoy!
